see that so clear!

00:52:57.560 --> 00:52:58.560
Why?

00:52:58.560 --> 00:52:59.560
You’ve been having a holiday or what?

00:52:59.560 --> 00:53:00.980
It’s horrible, absolutely!

00:53:00.980 --> 00:53:04.610
Very badly caught up!

00:53:04.610 --> 00:53:06.430
What’s the matter?

00:53:06.430 --> 00:53:10.360
You had a bad cold?

00:53:10.360 --> 00:53:13.130
Come here!

00:53:13.130 --> 00:53:18.310
I have never seen you being caught that much.

00:53:18.310 --> 00:53:35.100
You had exposed yourself I think [it was]
the sunning or what happened?

00:53:35.100 --> 00:53:42.300
Terrible!

00:53:42.300 --> 00:53:49.510
Better?

00:53:49.510 --> 00:53:50.510
Be careful!

00:53:50.510 --> 00:54:00.370
You see, these days it’s very sunny, looks
sunny, but maybe…You have to look after

00:54:00.370 --> 00:54:02.810
yourself.

00:54:02.810 --> 00:54:19.870
This country is full of this problem.

00:54:19.870 --> 00:54:24.750
Now better.

00:54:24.750 --> 00:54:29.630
What’s it?

00:54:29.630 --> 00:54:32.060
Vishuddhi.

00:54:32.060 --> 00:54:42.470
It rises from Vishuddhi to this.

00:54:42.470 --> 00:54:43.470
Haa!

00:54:43.470 --> 00:54:44.470
Better now.

00:54:44.470 --> 00:54:51.440
You sit or a while and it will work out in
the…You see it rises from the Vishuddhi

00:54:51.440 --> 00:54:52.440
to the.

00:54:52.440 --> 00:54:57.820
I think you caught cold very badly.

00:54:57.820 --> 00:54:59.950
What happened?

00:54:59.950 --> 00:55:05.270
Gavin Brown: I don’t know.

00:55:05.270 --> 00:55:14.970
Shri Mataji: I think you put your hand here.

00:55:14.970 --> 00:55:17.690
Sit down!

00:55:17.690 --> 00:55:18.690
Be careful.

00:55:18.690 --> 00:55:19.690
Hmm!

00:55:19.690 --> 00:55:20.690
Better.

00:55:20.690 --> 00:55:21.690
Somebody with cold must have come or something
you see, or the hay fever is there.

00:55:21.690 --> 00:55:23.330
Gavin Brown: Might be that.

00:55:23.330 --> 00:55:30.110
Shri Mataji: From Right Nabhi: it’s on the
right hand side the problem is.

00:55:30.110 --> 00:55:34.680
How are you?

00:55:34.680 --> 00:55:38.030
Good!

00:55:38.030 --> 00:55:58.180
Now close your eyes, close.

00:55:58.180 --> 00:56:10.270
You put your hand here, the right, and the
left there to work out the Vishuddhi.

00:56:10.270 --> 00:56:12.910
Right Nabhi also.

00:56:12.910 --> 00:56:16.860
Is it your liver coming up or what?

00:56:16.860 --> 00:56:23.860
Gavin Brown: I don’t think so.

00:56:23.860 --> 00:56:30.850
Shri Mataji: Quite a lot eh?

00:56:30.850 --> 00:56:34.350
Gavin Brown: Hmm.

00:56:34.350 --> 00:56:44.420
Shri Mataji: All right, move from the left
more, from the left.

