Press it hard!

01:04:26.960 --> 01:04:32.120
Better!

01:04:32.120 --> 01:04:55.890
Still you are working with the liver patients
are they?

01:04:55.890 --> 01:04:57.700
Doctor: Hmm.

01:04:57.700 --> 01:05:01.340
Shri Mataji: What do you do about them?

01:05:01.340 --> 01:05:06.100
What treatments do you give for liver patients
in the hospitals?

01:05:06.100 --> 01:05:08.070
Doctor: Special drugs.

01:05:08.070 --> 01:05:09.620
Shri Mataji: What drugs?

01:05:09.620 --> 01:05:11.700
Doctor: Depends what the problem is with the
liver.

01:05:11.700 --> 01:05:29.250
Shri Mataji: But still what drugs normally
you use?

01:05:29.250 --> 01:05:35.860
Doctor: The main things they use are for someone
who is alcoholic and they start to bleed.

01:05:35.860 --> 01:05:37.020
Shri Mataji: Alcohol?

01:05:37.020 --> 01:05:41.680
Doctor: They have alcoholic cirrhosis and
they bleed and they vomit blood.

01:05:41.680 --> 01:05:42.850
Shri Mataji: Really?

01:05:42.850 --> 01:05:43.850
That serious?

01:05:43.850 --> 01:05:47.510
Doctor: So we have special drugs to help stop
that.

01:05:47.510 --> 01:05:49.840
Shri Mataji: Just look at this!

01:05:49.840 --> 01:05:51.810
Despite that, nobody publishes these things.

01:05:51.810 --> 01:05:58.840
You know, the other day in a very so-called
important dinner table, there was a big argument

01:05:58.840 --> 01:06:07.240
[that] was on that, in France, the pubs are
open all the time, while here they open very

01:06:07.240 --> 01:06:12.150
late, so people are very unhappy that you
are not sufficiently alcoholic!

01:06:12.150 --> 01:06:14.970
A big discussion is on.

01:06:14.970 --> 01:06:16.570
Let them see these photographs!

01:06:16.570 --> 01:06:23.430
Why not show them how people vomit blood and
how people do these things.

01:06:23.430 --> 01:06:29.109
It would be a good idea.

01:06:29.109 --> 01:06:30.109
And the food they eat do they?

01:06:30.109 --> 01:06:36.090
Doctor: Well, there’s so many different
problems we have with the liver.

01:06:36.090 --> 01:06:42.037
Say, they are alcoholic then they have intravenous
therapy.

01:06:42.037 --> 01:06:43.037
Shri Mataji: They cannot eat the food?

01:06:43.037 --> 01:06:44.037
They vomit?

01:06:44.037 --> 01:06:45.037
Doctor: So they put special tubes down them
to stop them vomiting, and then they give

01:06:45.037 --> 01:06:45.537
them blood because they are losing so much.
